quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  67,15,"Ni We waborohereje isi; ngaho nimutambagire mu mpande zayo (zinyuranye), ndetse murye mu mafunguro ye (Allah). Kandi iwe ni ho muzazurwa mugana"
  67,16,Ese muratekanye (yemwe bahakanyi) ku buryo (mwizeye ko) uri mu ijuru (Allah) atabarigitisha mu isi ikabamira? Dore izaba iri gutigita
  67,17,Cyangwa se muratekanye ku buryo (mwizeye ko) uri mu ijuru ataboherereza inkubi y’umuyaga uvanze n’amabuye (wabarimbura mwese)? Ubwo ni bwo muzamenya uko ukuburira kwanjye (kumeze)
  67,18,Rwose ababayeho mbere yabo (abahakanyi b’i Maka) barahinyuye. Mbega uko uburakari bwanjye bwari bumeze
  67,19,Ese ntibabona inyoni hejuru yabo uko ziguruka zirambura amababa yazo zikanayahina? Ntawe uzifata (ngo zitagwa hasi) usibye (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe. Mu by’ukuri ni Ubona buri kintu bihebuje
  67,20,Ahubwo se uwo ni nde wababera ingabo (mwa bahakanyi mwe) ngo abatabare usibye (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe? Nyamara Abahakanyi baribeshya
  67,21,"Cyangwa se uwo ni nde wabaha amafunguro, (Allah) aramutse ahagaritse amafunguro ye? Ahubwo (abahakanyi) bakomeje gutsimbarara mu gasuzuguro no kwanga (ukuri)"
  67,22,Ese wa wundi ugenda yubitse umutwe (ahuzagurika) ni we wayobotse kurusha wa wundi ugenda yemye mu nzira igororotse
  67,23,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “(Allah) ni We wabaremye, abaha ukumva (amatwi), amaso n’imitima (ibafasha gutekereza); ariko mushimira gake!”"
  67,24,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ni We wabakwirakwije ku isi, kandi iwe ni ho muzakoranyirizwa.”"
  67,25,"Baranavuga bati “Ese iryo sezerano (izuka) rizaba ryari, niba koko muri abanyakuri?”"
  67,26,"Vuga uti “Mu by’ukuri ubumenyi (bw’igihe iryo zuka rizabera) buri kwa Allah, kandi njye ndi umuburizi ugaragara.”"
  67,27,"Ariko ubwo bazabibona (ibihano byo ku munsi w’imperuka) biri hafi, uburanga bw’abahakanye buzijima bugire agahinda, maze babwirwe bati “Ngibi ibyo mwajyaga musaba ko byihutishwa (ngaho byaje)!”"
  67,28,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Nimumbwire! Allah aramutse anyoretse njye n’abo turi kumwe (nk’uko mubyifuza) cyangwa akatugirira impuhwe, ni nde warinda abahakanyi ibihano bibabaza?”"
  67,29,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ni We (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe, twaramwemeye kandi ni na We twiringira. Vuba aha bidatinze muzamenya uri mu buyobe bugaragara (ibihano nibigera).”"
  67,30,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Nimumbwire! Amazi yanyu (mukoresha) aramutse arigitiye ikuzimu (agakama), ni nde (utari Allah) wabagarurira amazi (y’isoko) atemba?”"